@startuml
title Sequence Diagram: publication of a document in Syllabus.uno

actor "Postman Client" as Client
participant "Repository Service\nport 9011" as Repository
participant "Document Service\nport 8011" as Document
database "In-memory data stores\nstudent_id = 11" as DB

Client -> Repository: POST /repository/publish\n{document_id: 1101}
activate Repository
Repository -> Document: GET /documents/1101
activate Document
Document -> DB: find document by id = 1101
DB --> Document: document data
Document --> Repository: 200 OK\n{student_id: 11, document: {...}}
deactivate Document
Repository -> DB: create repository record
DB --> Repository: saved record
Repository --> Client: 200 OK\n{student_id: 11, record: {...}}
deactivate Repository

Client -> Repository: GET /repository/records
activate Repository
Repository -> DB: get all repository records
DB --> Repository: records list
Repository --> Client: 200 OK\n{student_id: 11, records: [...]}
deactivate Repository
@enduml
